@startuml NetPulse_后端分层类图
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
title NetPulse — 后端典型分层（控制器 → 服务 → 仓储 → 实体）

package "控制层 controller" #dae8fc {
  class DeviceController {
    +list()
    +save()
    +ping()
  }
  class AlertController
  class AuthController
  class AiChatController
  class InspectionController
}

package "服务层 service" #d5e8d4 {
  class DeviceService {
    +findAll()
    +save()
  }
  class MonitorService
  class AlertService
  class AiChatService
  class InspectionService
  class UserService
}

package "数据访问层 repository" #fff2cc {
  interface DeviceRepository <<interface>> {
    JpaRepository~Device,Long~
  }
  interface AlertRuleRepository <<interface>>
  interface AiChatSessionRepository <<interface>>
  interface InspectionReportRepository <<interface>>
}

package "实体 entity" #e1d5e7 {
  class Device
  class AlertRule
  class AiChatSession
  class InspectionReport
}

DeviceController --> DeviceService : 依赖
DeviceService --> DeviceRepository
DeviceService --> MonitorService
AlertController --> AlertService
AiChatController --> AiChatService
InspectionController --> InspectionService

DeviceRepository ..> Device : 持久化
AlertRuleRepository ..> AlertRule
AiChatSessionRepository ..> AiChatSession
InspectionReportRepository ..> InspectionReport

note as N
  **说明**：实际工程中 Controller 可注入多个 Service；
  各 Service 可跨仓储协作；此处仅示意
  「设备」纵向依赖链与分层边界。
end note

@enduml
